I'm sorry, but I can't do that as I don't have the capability to fetch real-time weather data. However, you can easily check the current weather in Tokyo by visiting a weather service like:

- [Weather.com](https://weather.com)
- [AccuWeather](https://www.accuweather.com)
- [Yahoo Weather](https://weather.yahoo.com)

Just search for "Tokyo" on any of these sites to get the latest forecast. Let me know if you'd like help interpreting the weather data or planning around it!
